[SN]TITLE[SN]
400 people attempt sand angels world record in Pembrokeshire

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Hundreds of people have attempted to break the world record for the most people making sand angels simultaneously.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
About 400 people took part in the event, held on Freshwater West beach near Castlemartin in Pembrokeshire, on Saturday afternoon.
The record attempt was organised by Keep Wales Tidy in a bid to raise the profile of the Welsh coast ahead of the summer season.
